<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:17:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国高级外交官预计印度将与乌克兰进行更多接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二在参议院听证会上回答有关印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪本月访问莫斯科的问题时表示，他预计很快就会有消息称印度正在加强与乌克兰的接触。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/top-us-diplomat-expects-more-indian-engagement-with-ukraine-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>欧莱雅二季度销量上升但中国市场低迷承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</link><description>法国化妆品巨头欧莱雅公布第二季度销售额增长 5.3%，低于预期，这可能进一步令本已担心重要的中国市场缺乏反弹的投资者感到不安。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:05:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/loreal-2q-sales-grow-53-slower-than-forecast-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>二号外交官表示，美国必须采取更多措施反击中国的行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国副国务卿库尔特·坎贝尔周二表示，华盛顿必须采取更多措施来对抗中国的行动，包括其建立军事基地的战略以及在非洲开采稀土矿的战略。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-must-do-more-counter-chinas-actions-no-2-diplomat-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国对伊朗导弹和无人机计划支持者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国周二对五名个人和七个实体实施制裁，财政部称这些人是伊朗导弹和无人机计划的协助者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-issues-sanctions-targeting-irans-missile-drone-program-facilitators-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球——中国队东京失利后王健林和孙杨夺得混双金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，在巴黎奥运会乒乓球混双决赛中，中国组合王楚钦/孙颖莎以4比2击败朝鲜组合李钟植/金锦勇，这是中国队横扫乒乓球项目金牌的第一步。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-wang-sun-win-mixed-doubles-gold-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>审计员称，奢华的国宴使法国总统陷入赤字</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</link><description>公共审计办公室表示，法国总统马克龙的办公室去年因取消为英国国王查尔斯举办的豪华龙虾晚宴和其他国宴而超支了数百万欧元。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:58:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavish-state-banquets-tip-french-presidency-into-red-auditor-says-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>Grifols 对中国投资减记 4.94 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</link><description>西班牙制药商 Grifols 已对其 2020 年至 2023 年的账目进行了 4.57 亿欧元（4.94 亿美元）的减记，以反映其所称的之前对其持有的中国上海莱士股份的会计处理不正确。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-revises-past-financial-records-with-equity-value-drop-494-mln-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国表示对中国征收新关税将至少推迟两周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</link><description>美国贸易代表办公室周二表示，美国对电动汽车及其电池、计算机芯片和医疗产品等一系列中国进口产品大幅提高关税的部分举措将至少推迟两周。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:39:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-start-new-china-tariffs-will-be-delayed-by-least-two-weeks-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>更多历史性的中国药检呈阳性给巴黎游泳运动蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</link><description>周二，《纽约时报》报道称，两名 2022 年游泳运动员的违禁类固醇检测呈阳性，但由于结果被归咎于受污染的食品，他们的临时禁赛被解除，中国因此再次陷入兴奋剂关注的焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 13:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/more-historic-china-positive-drug-tests-cast-cloud-over-paris-swimming-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国帮助意大利布雷博克服汽车行业的疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-posts-stable-margins-tough-market-shares-rise-2024-07-30/</link><description>意大利高级制动器制造商布雷博周二公布，上半年核心盈利和收入温和增长，其亚洲市场及其业务有助于维护老旧车辆，帮助应对汽车行业黯淡的前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:30:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italys-brembo-posts-stable-margins-tough-market-shares-rise-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>习近平祝贺委内瑞拉总统马杜罗连任</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-congratulates-venezuelas-maduro-reelection-2024-07-30/</link><description>官方媒体周二称，中国国家主席习近平祝贺委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗再次当选总统，这与一些拉美领导人和美国表达的怀疑和批评形成鲜明对比。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-congratulates-venezuelas-maduro-reelection-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>基辅欢迎与北京的对话，暗示泽连斯基与习近平可能举行会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kyiv-invites-chinese-foreign-minister-visit-ukraine-2024-07-30/</link><description>基辅外交部周二表示，乌克兰已邀请中国外长访问，对话不断加强，最终可能导致两国领导人举行会晤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:41:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kyiv-invites-chinese-foreign-minister-visit-ukraine-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>对默克公司加德西在中国销售的担忧导致股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-second-quarter-tops-street-view-strong-keytruda-sales-2024-07-30/</link><description>默克公司周二表示，第二季度其Gardasil疫苗在重要的中国市场的出货量下降，引发投资者担忧，其股价暴跌逾9%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 10:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/merck-second-quarter-tops-street-view-strong-keytruda-sales-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国证监会执法局长晋升为副主席</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-regulator-likely-promote-law-enforcement-chief-vice-chair-sources-2024-07-30/</link><description>中国证券监管机构周二将其执法负责人提升为副主席，突显北京方面加强对其5.1万亿美元股市监管的决心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:15:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-regulator-likely-promote-law-enforcement-chief-vice-chair-sources-2024-07-30/</guid></item><item><title>香港、澳门外国旅游团可免签进入海南</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</link><description>据官方媒体周二报道，中国国家移民管理局表示，来自香港和澳门的两人或两人以上的外国旅游团可以免签在中国海南省停留最多六天。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-tour-groups-hong-kong-macau-can-enter-hainan-without-visa-2024-07-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>